com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.ui.factories

Class BootstrapViewElements

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.ui.factories.BootstrapViewElements

  • public class BootstrapViewElements
extends Object
    Entry point for creating a bootstrap ViewElement control. An equivalent BootstrapViewElementBuilders class has been provided to create ViewElementBuilder and this is available as builders.

    For example to create a select element you can use: BootstrapViewElements.bootstrap.select() for a ViewElement, or BootstrapViewElements.bootstrap.builders.options() to configure a ViewElementBuilder.

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Stijn Vanhoof
